NOTE Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.280
Shri Mataji has asked me to share with you what

00:00:02.440 --> 00:00:08.160
was the last experience of Her Divine visit in Russia.

00:00:08.320 --> 00:00:13.560
And I must say it was really a dramatic breakthrough,

00:00:13.720 --> 00:00:22.120
because in the scientific conference She had in Moscow,

00:00:22.800 --> 00:00:27.120
there was the participation of a very well known scientist,

00:00:27.480 --> 00:00:28.840
a physicist.

00:00:29.000 --> 00:00:34.400
His name is Anatoli Akimov, he is very well known

00:00:34.560 --> 00:00:37.760
all over Russia and all over the world also.

00:00:37.920 --> 00:00:43.360
And he came with a theory and he has been studying

00:00:43.520 --> 00:00:45.320
this theory for a few years,

00:00:45.480 --> 00:00:50.720
which is based on the vacuum body and he studied

00:00:50.880 --> 00:00:54.960
something like the torsion fields and he could explain

00:00:55.120 --> 00:00:59.040
in a very clear way, in a very scientific way,

00:00:59.520 --> 00:01:03.880
the vibrations that Shri Mataji is emitting.

00:01:04.040 --> 00:01:08.320
So, at the beginning he was studying some Yogis

00:01:08.480 --> 00:01:13.520
which were meditating and he could notice that

00:01:13.680 --> 00:01:17.720
they were emitting vibrations,

00:01:17.880 --> 00:01:19.960
there was an aura around them.

00:01:20.120 --> 00:01:21.920
But then, when he came to Shri Mataji,

00:01:22.080 --> 00:01:26.680
when he saw Her pictures, the miraculous pictures,

00:01:26.840 --> 00:01:31.440
then he could really find out what it was and he said

00:01:31.600 --> 00:01:37.360
that in Her case, it was something which is infinite,

00:01:37.520 --> 00:01:39.360
which is unlimited.

00:01:39.520 --> 00:01:43.160
And also it was very nice, because at one point he said:

00:01:43.320 --> 00:01:48.120
"As a man of science, I have to admit that

00:01:48.280 --> 00:01:53.720
all the scientists that so far made some exceptional,

00:01:53.880 --> 00:01:56.200
unique discovery...,

00:01:56.360 --> 00:02:01.680
I have to admit that all this did not come

00:02:01.840 --> 00:02:05.640
through some scientific process, through the brain,

00:02:05.800 --> 00:02:06.920
we can say.

00:02:07.080 --> 00:02:13.120
But it come only through some divine inspiration.

00:02:13.280 --> 00:02:18.680
We can mention Newton, we can mention Einstein and so on."

00:02:18.840 --> 00:02:22.960
And he said: "Also in my case, when I was studying

00:02:23.160 --> 00:02:26.000
and working on this theory, at some point

00:02:26.160 --> 00:02:28.600
when I saw the picture of Shri Mataji

00:02:28.760 --> 00:02:30.480
then I got the inspiration."

00:02:30.640 --> 00:02:34.280
And then now Shri Mataji has invited him

00:02:34.440 --> 00:02:36.960
in September to come.

00:02:37.120 --> 00:02:40.680
And he has already written a book in Russia

00:02:40.840 --> 00:02:44.120
which will be translated in English and he is preparing

00:02:44.280 --> 00:02:49.920
a new book on which of course the major topic will be

00:02:50.080 --> 00:02:52.080
this unique discovery.

00:02:52.240 --> 00:02:54.520
So now we have somebody

00:02:54.680 --> 00:02:59.760
who has scientifically proved what Shri Mataji is.

00:03:20.880 --> 00:03:30.160
In Russia the people somehow are very open-minded.

00:03:30.320 --> 00:03:32.160
Not only that,

00:03:32.320 --> 00:03:36.520
the scientists specially are very open-minded

00:03:36.680 --> 00:03:39.280
and were suppressed very much,

00:03:39.440 --> 00:03:43.680
so they tried to find out

00:03:43.840 --> 00:03:45.920
the subtler things;

00:03:46.080 --> 00:03:52.440
not only finding out about chemicals

00:03:52.600 --> 00:03:58.720
or about some physical properties of the light,

00:03:58.880 --> 00:04:04.200
but they wanted to go into the subtler side.

00:04:04.360 --> 00:04:06.920
And they had find, found out

00:04:07.080 --> 00:04:13.000
already a great deal of knowledge

00:04:13.160 --> 00:04:16.120
about the auras -- auras around the hand,

00:04:16.280 --> 00:04:17.920
auras around the body --

00:04:18.080 --> 00:04:21.080
they had done so much of research

00:04:21.240 --> 00:04:25.680
and it was accepted all over the world, their findings.

00:04:25.840 --> 00:04:29.040
Now this gentleman was a specialist, I think,

00:04:29.200 --> 00:04:32.800
because he's a very well-known, very, very well-known person

00:04:32.960 --> 00:04:35.520
and he's holding a very big position.

00:04:35.680 --> 00:04:40.440
He was saying that he was, he has to run 150 organizations --

00:04:40.600 --> 00:04:43.680
very humble and very nice person.

00:04:43.840 --> 00:04:49.120
And when he came out with this discovery

00:04:49.360 --> 00:04:54.600
I was happy in a way, because scientifically if it is proved,

00:04:54.760 --> 00:04:56.920
then nobody can challenge it.

00:04:57.080 --> 00:05:00.760
He has already written a book with all the algebraical

00:05:00.920 --> 00:05:04.360
complications of what he wanted to prove.

00:05:04.520 --> 00:05:07.160
And he said there is a vacuum,

00:05:07.320 --> 00:05:09.760
beyond the consciousness there's vacuum,

00:05:09.920 --> 00:05:14.680
and in that vacuum only you can know the reality.

00:05:14.840 --> 00:05:19.560
And once all this becomes the reality it is a science,

00:05:19.720 --> 00:05:22.600
and that's how it is made into science.

00:05:22.760 --> 00:05:25.720
He showed so many of My photographs,

00:05:25.880 --> 00:05:29.400
specially the one where lot of energy is coming out

00:05:29.560 --> 00:05:32.560
of My Sahasrara when we are on a boat.

00:05:32.840 --> 00:05:37.120
So he said, "She is the Source of all the cosmic energy."

00:05:37.280 --> 00:05:39.920
And that's what is Adi Shakti is:

00:05:40.080 --> 00:05:44.240
She's the one who creates everything.

00:05:44.560 --> 00:05:51.640
The whole atmosphere that we know of is very artificial,

00:05:51.800 --> 00:05:55.560
but when you understand what She has done ...

00:05:55.720 --> 00:05:59.240
The first thing She does is to --

00:05:59.400 --> 00:06:02.560
in My book also I have written down about it,

00:06:02.720 --> 00:06:05.640
but I would like to tell you -- that Her first,

00:06:05.800 --> 00:06:12.640
should say, manifestation is on the left-hand side.

00:06:12.800 --> 00:06:16.680
That's the Mahakali's manifestation.

00:06:16.840 --> 00:06:22.160
So She comes on the Mahakali system, the left-hand side,

00:06:22.320 --> 00:06:26.960
and that is where She created Ganesha.

00:06:27.120 --> 00:06:32.040
Shri Ganesha is created because His purity,

00:06:32.200 --> 00:06:36.480
His innocence and auspiciousness,

00:06:36.640 --> 00:06:41.600
this had to be created before She created the universe.

00:06:41.760 --> 00:06:45.440
So first thing She does is to create Shri Ganesha,

00:06:45.600 --> 00:06:47.760
and He's settled down.

00:06:47.920 --> 00:06:51.520
Then She goes up, of course in the body of the Virata,

00:06:51.680 --> 00:06:54.680
and then She goes round and goes up

00:06:54.840 --> 00:06:58.000
on the right-hand side in the other way;

00:06:58.160 --> 00:07:02.280
and there She creates all the universes --

00:07:02.440 --> 00:07:04.920
as you call them, bhuvanas.

00:07:05.080 --> 00:07:10.200
One universe -- there are fourteen bhuvanas -- means

00:07:10.360 --> 00:07:15.480
these many, many universes make one bhuvana.

00:07:15.640 --> 00:07:18.320
And She creates all these things

00:07:18.480 --> 00:07:20.560
on the right-hand side.

00:07:20.720 --> 00:07:25.160
Then She goes up and then She descends down,

00:07:25.320 --> 00:07:27.440
creating all the chakras,

00:07:27.600 --> 00:07:30.240
the Adi Chakras or the peethas.

00:07:30.400 --> 00:07:33.400
She comes down, makes all these peethas

00:07:33.560 --> 00:07:37.800
and then She's settled as the Kundalini.

00:07:37.960 --> 00:07:42.640
But Adi Shakti is not fully the Kundalini, we can say,

00:07:42.800 --> 00:07:46.200
Kundalini is, is a part of it.

00:07:46.360 --> 00:07:50.160
The rest of the work is much more than this.

00:07:50.320 --> 00:07:52.680
So the, all the, we call it the residual energy --

00:07:52.840 --> 00:07:55.680
means after going through all this journey,

00:07:55.840 --> 00:08:00.400
then She comes round and She goes as Kundalini.

00:08:00.560 --> 00:08:04.640
Because of this Kundalini and the chakras,

00:08:04.800 --> 00:08:09.320
She creates a area which we call

00:08:09.480 --> 00:08:13.720
as the chakras in the body.

00:08:13.880 --> 00:08:17.400
Now first She creates these chakras in the head:

00:08:17.560 --> 00:08:20.240
we call them the peethas of the chakras.

00:08:20.400 --> 00:08:23.880
And then She comes down and creates these chakras,

00:08:24.040 --> 00:08:28.680
which are in the body of the Virata.

00:08:28.840 --> 00:08:30.920
Now once this has happened,

00:08:31.080 --> 00:08:35.800
then She creates human beings, but not directly:

00:08:35.960 --> 00:08:39.480
through the evolutionary process She goes through,

00:08:39.640 --> 00:08:42.160
and that's how the evolution starts.

00:08:42.320 --> 00:08:49.080
And then it starts developing from the minute,

00:08:49.240 --> 00:08:53.280
small little microscopic organisms in the water,

00:08:53.440 --> 00:08:57.360
and then it starts evolving.

00:08:57.520 --> 00:08:59.560
So when She creates water and

00:08:59.720 --> 00:09:01.600
She creates all the universes,

00:09:01.760 --> 00:09:05.080
She chooses this Mother Earth as the best place

00:09:05.240 --> 00:09:07.840
to play Her evolutionary process,

00:09:08.000 --> 00:09:12.400
and there She makes this little microscopic thing.

00:09:12.560 --> 00:09:14.640
Of course I have written all about it,

00:09:14.800 --> 00:09:17.160
and when My book will be released

00:09:17.320 --> 00:09:21.480
you can see that how first hydrogen,

00:09:21.640 --> 00:09:24.960
carbon and oxygen and all of these things

00:09:25.120 --> 00:09:28.240
were mixed up and how nitrogen comes into play,

00:09:28.400 --> 00:09:31.400
and how a living process starts.

00:09:31.560 --> 00:09:34.200
All this I have done it in My another book

00:09:34.360 --> 00:09:35.920
that I am going to write now.

00:09:36.080 --> 00:09:37.480
I mean, I have mostly finished,

00:09:37.640 --> 00:09:40.240
but there's some more chakras are to be dealt with.

00:09:40.400 --> 00:09:42.520
Now with this happening, you see,

00:09:42.680 --> 00:09:45.240
one thing is there that whatever I write,

00:09:45.400 --> 00:09:47.240
now people won't doubt.

00:09:47.400 --> 00:09:49.480
They will know it's a scientific fact,

00:09:49.640 --> 00:09:53.040
and that's what whatever I say is a fact.

00:09:53.200 --> 00:09:55.560
Now to believe in the car...

00:09:55.720 --> 00:10:02.800
in the, even, a Mother, Adi Shakti, was impossible.

00:10:02.960 --> 00:10:06.320
Specially you'll be amazed that Christian religion

00:10:06.480 --> 00:10:09.760
somehow or other avoided the mentioning of the Mother.

00:10:09.920 --> 00:10:12.880
Then the Islam, that also avoided

00:10:13.040 --> 00:10:15.200
the mentioning of the Mother.

00:10:15.360 --> 00:10:18.920
There's completely negation towards the Mother.

00:10:19.080 --> 00:10:22.840
But only Indian philosophy had the Mother,

00:10:23.000 --> 00:10:26.400
and the Indians are actually Shakti-worshippers.

00:10:26.560 --> 00:10:29.080
So this is how it was kept up

00:10:29.240 --> 00:10:33.240
and brought to this position now,

00:10:33.400 --> 00:10:39.440
that people have got, people have got full idea

00:10:39.600 --> 00:10:45.480
as to Mother Principle that has worked out everything.

00:10:45.640 --> 00:10:48.680
On this Mother Principle in India people are very sure

00:10:48.840 --> 00:10:51.160
that it's the Mother who does everything,

00:10:51.320 --> 00:10:55.760
and thus we have in India many, we should say,

00:10:55.920 --> 00:10:58.960
many swayambus, means things

00:10:59.120 --> 00:11:01.600
that are created of the Mother Earth.

00:11:01.760 --> 00:11:04.400
For example, you know in Maharashtra

00:11:04.560 --> 00:11:06.920
we have got Mahakali's place,

00:11:07.080 --> 00:11:09.280
Mahasaraswati, Mahalakshmi,

00:11:09.440 --> 00:11:14.440
and also we have got a place for the Adi Shakti.

00:11:14.600 --> 00:11:16.640
Some people who have been to Nasik

00:11:16.800 --> 00:11:19.960
must have seen Chaturshringi.

00:11:20.120 --> 00:11:22.680
How many people have you been to Chaturshringi,

00:11:22.840 --> 00:11:26.600
out of you? -- it's good.

00:11:27.760 --> 00:11:33.360
So this Chaturshringi represents the Adi Shakti:

00:11:33.840 --> 00:11:42.080
Adi Shakti which is the fourth dimension of this Power,

00:11:42.240 --> 00:11:44.480
which gives you the ascent.

00:11:44.640 --> 00:11:48.240
And ultimately through Mahalakshmi channel only,

00:11:48.400 --> 00:11:50.400
you get your realization.

00:11:50.560 --> 00:11:54.320
All this is a process,

00:11:54.480 --> 00:11:59.000
all was created by the power of Adi Shakti.

00:11:59.160 --> 00:12:01.760
It's a tremendous task.

00:12:01.920 --> 00:12:05.120
The previous ones were not difficult,

00:12:05.280 --> 00:12:09.920
because there for nature to create it was very easy.

00:12:10.080 --> 00:12:13.000
The Mother Earth is one with the Adi Shakti,

00:12:13.160 --> 00:12:16.040
the whole atmosphere is one with the Adi Shakti,

00:12:16.200 --> 00:12:18.560
all the elements are one with the Adi Shakti,

00:12:18.720 --> 00:12:22.160
so She could create all that without any difficulties.

00:12:22.320 --> 00:12:26.960
But when human beings came, they got their freedom.

00:12:27.880 --> 00:12:30.880
That's the only, I should say, the species

00:12:31.040 --> 00:12:35.000
which fell into the maya of thinking

00:12:35.160 --> 00:12:40.080
and of having the ego in them.

00:12:40.240 --> 00:12:44.400
With this ego a maya worked on them, I should say,

00:12:44.560 --> 00:12:48.520
and they forgot about the Principle

00:12:48.680 --> 00:12:51.480
that created this universe --

00:12:51.640 --> 00:12:53.200
they took it for granted.

00:12:53.360 --> 00:12:55.560
They felt that this is their own right

00:12:55.720 --> 00:12:58.800
that they are there, this is their own achievement

00:12:58.960 --> 00:13:01.880
and they are the owners of everything.

00:13:02.040 --> 00:13:05.000
This started working in their minds so much

00:13:05.160 --> 00:13:07.160
that they invaded other countries,

00:13:07.320 --> 00:13:09.080
they destroyed so many people and

00:13:09.240 --> 00:13:11.640
they never felt bad about it.

00:13:11.800 --> 00:13:15.200
All their lives they have been thinking about aggressing others,

00:13:15.360 --> 00:13:19.240
controlling others and doing all kinds of harmful things.

00:13:19.400 --> 00:13:23.200
But they never even thought or

00:13:23.440 --> 00:13:26.240
never did any introspection to see that

00:13:26.400 --> 00:13:28.760
what we are doing is very, very wrong

00:13:28.920 --> 00:13:31.040
and it should not be done.

00:13:31.200 --> 00:13:33.280
Because of the freedom they have,

00:13:33.440 --> 00:13:35.480
there's such a turmoil in this world.

00:13:35.640 --> 00:13:39.320
And the people who were in charge of affairs,

00:13:39.480 --> 00:13:43.360
they were very, very cruel and extremely --

00:13:43.520 --> 00:13:48.160
had no feelings for the other people.

00:13:48.320 --> 00:13:52.480
And this happened so many times in the, on this earth.

00:13:52.720 --> 00:13:56.320
Now Sahaja Yoga has started.

00:13:56.480 --> 00:13:58.240
Once Sahaja Yoga has started,

00:13:58.400 --> 00:14:02.400
we have Sahaja yogis who are now receiving

00:14:02.560 --> 00:14:06.120
the blessings of the Adi Shakti directly.

00:14:06.280 --> 00:14:09.320
But still I must say, among Sahaja yogis also

00:14:09.480 --> 00:14:16.480
we don't have people whom I would call as very well-matured.

00:14:16.640 --> 00:14:19.760
They are Sahaja yogis, some of them, are just because

00:14:19.920 --> 00:14:24.560
it's a fashion; maybe it should be better from their angle,

00:14:24.720 --> 00:14:27.800
or from their selfish angle or whatever it is.

00:14:27.960 --> 00:14:29.400
Is a very wrong thing.

00:14:29.560 --> 00:14:32.360
If you are in Sahaja Yoga you must know now

00:14:32.520 --> 00:14:36.480
you are responsible for the whole world.

00:14:36.640 --> 00:14:40.200
You are the only people who have come forward,

00:14:40.360 --> 00:14:43.720
you are the only people who have achieved something.

00:14:43.880 --> 00:14:45.960
And then at this juncture

00:14:46.120 --> 00:14:48.600
you should behave in a manner that,

00:14:48.760 --> 00:14:53.440
that behooves a big saint or a realized soul;

00:14:53.600 --> 00:14:57.120
but sometimes you find them behaving in such a manner,

00:14:57.280 --> 00:14:59.160
is shocking sometimes.

00:14:59.320 --> 00:15:03.200
They have no respect for themselves or for others,

00:15:03.360 --> 00:15:06.400
and their whole attitude is very funny.

00:15:06.560 --> 00:15:10.400
Some of them are money-oriented, some of them are power-oriented.

00:15:10.560 --> 00:15:13.640
And those who are power-oriented are more dangerous, I think,

00:15:13.800 --> 00:15:15.320
than money-oriented;

00:15:15.480 --> 00:15:17.760
because those who are power-oriented

00:15:17.920 --> 00:15:22.920
try to bring such bad name to Sahaja Yoga.

00:15:23.160 --> 00:15:27.800
They are very insulting, dominating and horrible people.

00:15:27.960 --> 00:15:33.000
Their whole attitude is to achieve power in Sahaja Yoga,

00:15:33.160 --> 00:15:36.200
and they try all tricks to achieve that power.

00:15:36.360 --> 00:15:39.520
But for some time they, they look all right --

00:15:39.680 --> 00:15:41.400
after some time you'll find

00:15:41.560 --> 00:15:44.960
they'll all disappear from the field of Sahaja Yoga.

00:15:45.120 --> 00:15:48.080
It's a very big cleansing process going on.

00:15:48.240 --> 00:15:53.120
You must understand that you have come in the,

00:15:53.280 --> 00:16:01.000
in the field of very high consciousness

00:16:01.160 --> 00:16:04.800
where you are in contact with the Divine.

00:16:04.960 --> 00:16:09.080
Now here if you behave like ordinary people

00:16:09.240 --> 00:16:11.400
who have no divinity within them,

00:16:11.560 --> 00:16:13.960
how long will you continue like this?

00:16:14.120 --> 00:16:19.080
So this is very important that you should try to meditate

00:16:19.240 --> 00:16:20.920
and evolve yourselves,

00:16:21.080 --> 00:16:25.000
and become really very good Sahaja yogis.

00:16:25.160 --> 00:16:28.040
In some places we are very, very lucky.

00:16:28.200 --> 00:16:31.280
In some, some countries we are very, very lucky.

00:16:31.440 --> 00:16:35.920
But in some countries I find the people are just deaf and dumb.

00:16:36.080 --> 00:16:38.880
They can't understand Sahaja Yoga.

00:16:39.040 --> 00:16:40.720
For My program they do come,

00:16:40.880 --> 00:16:43.080
and afterwards just they disappear.

00:16:43.240 --> 00:16:46.120
This one I think is also --

00:16:46.280 --> 00:16:48.720
Sahaja yogis are responsible for this.

00:16:48.880 --> 00:16:50.440
The way they go about,

00:16:50.600 --> 00:16:56.400
the way they want to do Sahaj work is not Sahaj.

00:16:56.560 --> 00:16:59.800
Must be something definitely wrong with the whole thing,

00:16:59.960 --> 00:17:04.160
and that's why it's not working out the same way

00:17:04.320 --> 00:17:07.000
as it is working out in many places.

00:17:07.160 --> 00:17:11.240
So I have to tell you that all this is there,

00:17:11.400 --> 00:17:13.200
that Adi Shakti is there,

00:17:13.360 --> 00:17:15.840
and all this has happened through Adi Shakti.

00:17:16.000 --> 00:17:19.160
But now the further work has to be done

00:17:19.320 --> 00:17:22.040
through you people because you are the channels,

00:17:22.200 --> 00:17:26.160
you are the one who have to transform people.

00:17:26.320 --> 00:17:29.240
Now everybody should understand and know

00:17:29.400 --> 00:17:34.880
how many people we have given realization.

00:17:35.120 --> 00:17:37.200
We have to think about it:

00:17:37.360 --> 00:17:40.160
what have we done for Sahaja Yoga?

00:17:40.320 --> 00:17:43.760
